snippet.title: Sonic Horizons - SAGE 2023 Teaser
snippet.description:
My open-world Sonic Fangame, “Sonic Horizons”, will have a full on demo at this year’s Sonic Amateurs Games Expo! Thought of uploading the trailer that was shown off at the trailer from a few days ago, hope you’re hyped for what’s to come at this year’s expo!

#SAGE2023 #sonic #sonicfangame
